{"id":310921,"type":6,"name":"布尔什维克兄弟","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/41/bb/310921_M7mMV.jpg","summary":"曾经被人称为“布尔什维克家庭”中的五个孩子——刘布、刘尔、刘什、刘维、刘克，由于家庭破裂，母亲含恨死去，父亲又被划为“右派”，生活的重担沉沉地压在了他们的肩上。几个失去父母之爱的“布尔什维克兄弟”依偎在姐姐刘布的臂膀下忍受贫穷和痛苦，终于长大成人。改革开放的大潮卷来时， “布尔什维克兄弟”之间有的升迁，有的落伍，有的声名显赫，有的默默无闻，每个人不同的经历、不同的遭遇、不同的个性，都同样在时代的潮流中碰撞沉浮，最终都找到了属于自己的人生。 ","info":"<li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/38889\">李幼斌</a>、傅学成、郑铮、田岷、陈瑾、雷汉</li><li><span>集数: </span>28</li><li><span>开始: </span>1995年</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 历史 / 家庭</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>语言: </span>汉语普通话</li><li><span>每集长: </span>45分钟</li><li><span>导演: </span>王冀邢</li><li><span>编剧: </span>王冀邢</li><li><span>制片人: </span>王冀邢</li><li><span>监制: </span>尤小刚、吴宝文、张仲炎</li><li><span>摄影: </span>罗逊</li><li><span>美术设计: </span>程金昶</li>","eps":[{"id":966243,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966243","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966244,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966244","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966245,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966245","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966246,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966246","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966247,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966247","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966248,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966248","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966249,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966249","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":966250,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/966250","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status